---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div style="max-width:700px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;">
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>
    <h2 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.8rem;">What we collect</h2>
    <p>xCrypto24 collects minimal anonymous data to improve the service:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:2;margin:0.5rem 0;">
      <li>Anonymous click interactions (element clicked, page URL)</li>
      <li>Device type, browser, and country (from headers)</li>
      <li>No personal names, emails, or accounts required</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.8rem;">What we don't collect</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:2;margin:0.5rem 0;">
      <li>No wallet addresses</li>
      <li>No financial information</li>
      <li>No personal identification</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.8rem;">Data usage</h2>
    <p>All data is used solely to improve features and understand usage patterns. We never sell data to third parties.</p>
    <h2 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.8rem;">Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use a localStorage identifier for anonymous session tracking. You can clear this anytime via your browser settings.</p>
    <h2 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.8rem;">Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? <a href="/contact" style="color:#3b82f6;">Contact us</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
